import {includes,get} from "lodash";
 
import React from "react";
import ReactDOM from "react-dom";
import { cx } from "emotion";
import PropTypes from "../utils/prop-types-extra";
import mergeProps from "../utils/merge-props";
import getChildren from "../utils/children";
 
import getInputStyle from "../styles/input/input.style";
import getInputLabelStyle from "../styles/input/input-label.style";
import getInputButtonStyle from "../styles/input/input-button.style";
import getInputIconStyle from "../styles/input/input-icon.style";
 
import {Icon} from "./icon";
 
 
function isButton(element) {
  return get(element, "type.isButton");
}
 
function isCorner(element) {
  return get(element, "type.isCorner");
}
 
function isTag(element) {
  return get(element, "type.isTag");
}
 
function isLabel(element) {
 
  return get(element,"type.isLabel");
}
 
function isInput(element) {
  return includes(["input","textarea"],element.type);
}
 
export default class Input extends React.Component {
 
  onInputRef = (el)=>{
    if (el) {
      this.inputElement = ReactDOM.findDOMNode(el); //eslint-disable-line react/no-find-dom-node
      if (this.inputElement) { this.onInputReady(this.inputElement); }
    }
    else {
      this.inputElement = null;
    }
  }
 
  onInputReady(el) {
    const {onInputReady} = this.props;
    if (onInputReady) {
      onInputReady(el);
    }
  }
 
  focus = ()=>{
    const {inputElement} = this;
    if (inputElement) {
      inputElement.focus();
    }
  }
 
  render() {
 
    const {
      loading,
      error,
      transparent,
      inverted,
      fluid,
      icon,
      iconLeft,
      iconProps,
      size,
      containerComponent,
      component: ignoreMe,
      containerProps: ignoreMe2,
      ...otherProps
    } = this.props;
 
    
    const component = this.props.component || ((this.props.type === "textarea" && "textarea") || "input");
    
    const styleFlags = {
      loading,
      error,
      transparent,
      inverted,
      fluid,
      icon: !!icon,
      iconLeft,
    };
 
    let children = getChildren(this) || [];
 
    let hadInput;
 
    children.forEach((child)=>{
      if (isInput(child)) {
        hadInput = true;
        return;
      }
      if (isLabel(child)) {
        styleFlags.labeled = true;
        styleFlags.labelRight = hadInput;
        styleFlags.labelLeft = !hadInput;
      }
      if (isCorner(child)) {
        styleFlags.cornerLabel = true;
      }
      if (isTag(child)) {
        styleFlags.tagLabel = true;
      }
      if (isButton(child)) {
        styleFlags.buttoned = true;
        styleFlags.buttonRight = hadInput;
        styleFlags.buttonLeft = !hadInput;
      }
    });
 
    if (!hadInput) { children.push(<input />); }
 
    let iconElement;
    if (icon || loading) {
 
      if (styleFlags.labeled || styleFlags.buttoned) {
        styleFlags.iconLeft = !(styleFlags.labelLeft || styleFlags.buttonLeft);
      }
 
      styleFlags.iconRight = !styleFlags.iconLeft;
 
      const newIconProps = mergeProps({
        key: "icon",
        "aria-hidden": true,
        className: cx("cm-input-icon",getInputIconStyle(styleFlags,size)),
      },iconProps);
 
      iconElement = <i {...newIconProps}><Icon icon={icon} /></i>;
 
    }
 
 
    children = children.map((child)=>{
 
      if (isLabel(child)) {
        return React.cloneElement(child,mergeProps({
          className: cx("cm-input-label", getInputLabelStyle(styleFlags, size)),
          left: styleFlags.labelLeft,
        },child.props));
      }
 
      if (isButton(child)) {
        return React.cloneElement(child, mergeProps({
          className: cx("cm-input-button", getInputButtonStyle(styleFlags, size)),
        }, child.props));
      }
 
      if (isInput(child)) {
 
        const inputProps = mergeProps(otherProps, {
          key: "input",
          children: null,
          ref: this.onInputRef,
        },child.props);
 
        const input = React.createElement(component,inputProps);
 
        if (iconElement && iconLeft) {
          return [iconElement,input];
        }
        if (iconElement) {
          return [input, iconElement];
        }
        return input;
      }
 
      return null;
 
    });
 
    const containerProps = mergeProps({
      className: cx("cm-input", getInputStyle(styleFlags,size)),
    },this.props.containerProps);
 
    return React.createElement(containerComponent,containerProps,children);
 
  }
 
}
 
Input.propTypes = {
  component: PropTypes.component,
  type: PropTypes.oneOfType([PropTypes.string,PropTypes.func]),
  size: PropTypes.string,
  icon: PropTypes.string,
  loading: PropTypes.bool,
  iconProps: PropTypes.object,
  iconLeft: PropTypes.bool,
  containerComponent: PropTypes.component,
  onInputReady: PropTypes.func,
};
 
Input.defaultProps = {
  containerComponent: "div",
  type: "text"
};
